    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given the explicitly bounded COU scope limited to ASTM F1717 compression-bending. All quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval <1.96, percent difference <10%) satisfied for all three QoIs across N=11 constructs at two independent laboratories. Overall credibility sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
